org.pititom.core is an useful java tools provider

Note :
	This library is under MIT license (see LICENSE file).

Provides :
	- generic event transmitter and handler (synchronous and asynchronous)
	- service loading based on package naming convension
	- extensible messenger
	- stream stack editor

Third party dependences : 
	- org.kohsuke.args4j (currently use 2.0.12, under MIT license)

Details of modules :
	- org.pititom.core
	- org.pititom.core.args4j           -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.parsing

	- org.pititom.core.messenger        -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j, org.pititom.core.service
	- org.pititom.core.messenger.stream -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j, org.pititom.core.messenger, org.pititom.core.stream
	- org.pititom.core.parsing          -> org.pititom.core
	- org.pititom.core.service          -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j, org.pititom.core.parsing, org.eclipse.core.runtime
	- org.pititom.core.stream           -> requires org.kohsuke.args4j, org.pititom.core, org.pititom.core.args4j

Helper modules:
	- org.pititom.core.service.eclipse  -> org.eclipse.core.runtime (this module is intended to be fragment of org.pititom.core.service for eclipse plateform use)

See test directory for samples
